profile: Barkley Carrier has almost 30 years of customer service and management experience leading teams in central Alberta. We're proud to provide professional Window Cleaning, Gutter Cleaning, House Washing, Pressure Washing, Snow Removal, and Christmas Light Installation services to Central Alberta, including Red Deer, Sundre, Olds, and all surrounding Central Alberta regions. We want each and every customer to become part of our Men In Kilts Family and we're determined to deliver a fantastic experience. Our mission is simple, and Barkley and team live it to the fullest... to bring smiles to the world, one kilt at a time. Just remember... No Peeking!
